       :total-files 45  ;; 00-cover + 00-manifest + 00-outline + 16 chapters + 26 appendices (a-z)
       :word-count 57598
       :target 60000
       :under-by 2402
       :status "STRUCTURE-COMPLETE PLUS-EXPANDED WORDS-NEAR-TARGET"
       :note "Book was NOT actually empty per audit; had extensive 32-file
              content authored 2026-07-16. Added manifest+outline for
              invariant tracking, plus 11 additional appendices (P-Z)
              expanding domains: fixed-point/decimal arithmetic, error
              propagation, timezones, percentages/rates, serialization,
              comparison recipes, validation, optionals, worked examples,
