  :status "PHASE-1-COMPLETE PHASE-2-STRUCTURE-COMPLETE PHASE-2-WORD-COUNTS-UNDER PHASE-3-COMPLETE"
  :recommendation-for-alfred
"Review the 4 new/expanded books. Decide on the 7 surfaced decisions.
Book-of-values is closest to spec (57k / 60k). Others under target on
word count but complete on structure. If word-count target is inviolable,
Wave 1.5 could focus on expansion. If structural completeness is
sufficient, Wave 2 should target book-of-reasoning-source (still empty)
and the 3 THIN books (systems, hellosurface, items-and-scenarios).

Do not commit any of this. Working tree is unstaged for review.")
